# 🚀 Resume Radar

AI-powered Resume Screening & ATS Match Analyzer built with FastAPI, Sentence Transformers, and LLMs.

---

## 📌 Features

- 📄 Upload multiple resumes (PDF, DOCX, TXT)
- 🎯 Compare resumes against Job Descriptions
- 🧠 Semantic similarity scoring using Sentence Transformers
- 🤖 LLM-powered ATS match analysis
- ✅ Matching & Missing Skills Detection
- 💡 Resume Improvement Suggestions
- ✍️ AI Resume Bullet Rewriter
- 📊 Resume Ranking
- 📝 Scan History using SQLite

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Backend
- FastAPI
- Python
- SQLite
- Sentence Transformers
- Scikit-learn
- OpenAI / Groq API

### Frontend
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

### AI Models
- all-MiniLM-L6-v2
- GPT-4o Mini / Llama 3.1 8B Instant

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```text
Resume-Radar/
│
├── backend/
│   ├── main.py
│   ├── database.py
│   ├── file_parser.py
│   ├── semantic_matcher.py
│   ├── llm_analyzer.py
│   └── history.db
│
├── frontend/
│   └── index.html
│
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
```

---

## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
git clone <repo-url>

cd Resume-Radar

pip install -r requirements
```

---

## ▶️ Run

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

Open:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000
```

---

## 🔍 Workflow

1. Upload Resume(s)
2. Paste Job Description
3. Semantic Similarity Calculation
4. LLM Resume Analysis
5. Skill Matching
6. ATS Match Score Generation
7. Resume Suggestions
8. Resume Ranking
9. Save Analysis History

